    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325200/extras/7d3e48d7ebd06031a0d912bddbdbdf0e.avif?t=1767524651\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325200/extras_big/7d3e48d7ebd06031a0d912bddbdbdf0e.avif?t=1767524651 width=800 height=322 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Long forgotten in the depths of the toy chest, Teddy—a loyal and courageous knight—is called to action. As chaos spreads across the toy world, driven by the vengeful Baba Yaga plushie and her sinister army, it’s up to Teddy to rise, face the darkness, and fight through haunted toys  to restore peace to the realm of playthings!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325200/extras/d973130c9dc3ddf63862f3536e2e80d6.avif?t=1767524651\" width=307 height=96 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325200/extras/b6a39874b2f7b49c502d25616ca3e212.poster.avif?t=1767524651\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325200/extras/b6a39874b2f7b49c502d25616ca3e212.webm?t=1767524651\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325200/extras/b6a39874b2f7b49c502d25616ca3e212.mp4?t=1767524651\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Physics-Powered Combat</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in fast-paced, physics-based battles that require strategy and reflexes, pushing enemies off platforms and knocking them back to the bottom of the toy chest. Each room offers unique opportunities for creative takedowns!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dash, Bounce, and Chain Combos</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by Smash Bros, Teddy Knight introduces bouncy physics to combat, letting you launch enemies in every direction and chain them into thrilling combo attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customize your playstyle</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect powerful upgrades, items, and abilities that allow you to build a unique approach to combat. Experiment with different strategies to match your playstyle and take on increasingly challenging foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325200/extras/5c10ad8fb899ae32fe6511b72e51e047.avif?t=1767524651\" width=408 height=96 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325200/extras/a8d53fea919241181c96d259d6139832.poster.avif?t=1767524651\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325200/extras/a8d53fea919241181c96d259d6139832.webm?t=1767524651\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325200/extras/a8d53fea919241181c96d259d6139832.mp4?t=1767524651\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progress through the sinister depths of the toy chest, where forgotten toys  create a world full of mystery. Each area offers unique challenges, hidden secrets, and an atmosphere that grows darker and more threatening as you progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325200/extras/8a12cd0dc356f2a056912c8d59c30ea5.avif?t=1767524651\" width=556 height=96 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rediscover each level in Nightmare Mode, where the difficulty ramps up and the atmosphere takes on an even darker, more ominous tone. Conquer this mode to unlock new abilities, challenges, and rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to brave the toy chest and face the darkness within? Grab your hammer, take a deep breath, and prepare to dash and bounce in Teddy Knight!</strong></p>",
